<!-- Who I Am -->
<section id="whoiam">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="title">
      Who We <span>Are</span>
    </h1>
    <h2 class="sub-title">
      We are a Colombian company, with 13 years of experience in the market, which offers fresh and affordable trends for every stage in a woman’s life.
    </h2>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6 first">
        <h4 class="heading turquoise"><i class="fa fa-suitcase"></i> Our <strong>Mission</strong>  </h4>
        <p>
          We’re a company committed in the design and marketing of clothing for each stage in a woman’s life. To achieve it, we are focused on transforming the product according to the demands in quality, technology and the market, it projects us on to the client as a versatile and accessible brand for modern women.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <h4 class="heading blue"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> Our <strong>Vision</strong></h4>  
        <p>
          Being a company positioned in the national and international market, we are focused on the production of high quality women's clothes, always in touch with the new trends, fashion and standards of a qualified team, that evaluate  the product in all of its stages, and to transform it into a relevant and accessible option for the modern woman.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h3 class="heading orange"><i class="fa fa-users"></i> Our <strong>Essence</strong></h3>
    
    <div class="add-md-top">
      <p>
        Lady’s , we understand that every stage of your life is one step closer to your personal fulfillment, so we design each of our garments trying to make your life calm, practical and fun. You are our inspiration, and we want your image to project the versatility and femininity that you care about so much.
      </p>
      <p>
        We know you are multifaceted and decisive in every moment of your life, and you are essential to your family, and a determinant in the company and a key in society, so we think that the choice you make will be the right one, when everything you earn reassures every situation in your development. Your growth is part of our history, so we will always offer you fresh and authentic trends that come in harmony with your style.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

